                  "adjusted_stars": 4.95475,
                  "stars": 5.0,
                  "text": "This place was absolutely incredible! I'll break down the whole experience. \n\nThe Decor: After talking to the owners, we found out that every single decor item is intentional and has meaning behind it. From the church pews that now act as comfy booths to the hats on the wall! All items, even the tables, were hand made by the owners. It gave us a new appreciation for the time and thought that went into every single inch of the restaurant. 5/5 Stars. \n\nThe Food: We have tried multiple Mexican restaurants around the Vegas strip and this is hands down the best we've ever had in Nevada. You can taste the freshness in every single bite. The owner informed us that everything is hand prepared fresh every day, nothing is ever frozen, and all recipes are top secret family recipes. The pollo and pastor was full of flavor, the chips were freshly made just for us, and every single salsa was to die for. 5/5 Stars. \n\nThe Service: The owners were right there to answer all of our questions. And we had A LOT. they were so helpful and went out of their way to make us feel important and appreciated. 5/5 Stars. \n\nThe experience: Absolutely love the DIY concept. Had everything we needed (and some) to make our tacos exactly how we wanted them! 5/5 Stars."
